{"tid":775422,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[長江後浪推前浪] TWICE打破少女時代最高銷量紀錄","createTime":"2018-08-11T06:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T07:51:38.000Z","uid":74065,"like":8,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5e3eee957c7e7ca2246532ed1e6860dee5a606e8","tid":775422,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:56:41.000Z","msg":"據韓國Gaon唱片銷量榜公布的最新數字顯示，女團TWICE上月初推出的新專輯《SummerNights》，至今累積銷量29.2萬張，成績理想。出道短短3年的TWICE，至今推出9張專輯，總銷量高達266.1萬張，超越少女時代發行12張專輯合共239.3萬張的紀錄，成為韓國女團最高銷量組合，少女時代跌落第2位，而排名第3的是總銷量66.5萬張的Red Velvet，第4位則是Apink，有63.7萬張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b2bbc6b7d6f5e7e107281bb476994ccf9c424c","tid":775422,"uid":132587,"like":41,"dislike":8,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:06:39.000Z","msg":"無少女時代會有宜家既kpop? 會有宜家既twice?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93486515c47d6fd7fea87bc305f6535baa34cae9","tid":775422,"uid":74065,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"25b2bbc6b7d6f5e7e107281bb476994ccf9c424c","tid":775422,"uid":132587,"like":41,"dislike":8,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:06:39.000Z","msg":"無少女時代會有宜家既kpop? 會有宜家既twice?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"冇世宗大王都冇少女時代"},{"pid":"86471c67d56e7fccacdcd5c890f91137a841ed33","tid":775422,"uid":34643,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:35:33.000Z","msg":"總銷量，冇意義"},{"pid":"9a584dd5a3937dd1476127e72248510b4f202be8","tid":775422,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86471c67d56e7fccacdcd5c890f91137a841ed33","tid":775422,"uid":34643,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:35:3